ğŸ“Œ Overview

This Terraform project provisions an Ubuntu EC2 instance on AWS and configures it as a fully functional Apache web server using Terraform file and remote-exec provisioners.

The deployment installs required packages, downloads a website template, and serves it automatically via Apache.

